      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Smart filly WISHING BELLE (8) added to a string of top-two finishes by beating the boys last week. Draws much wider but her record at this circuit and distance stands at six wins and a placing from seven attempts and she is nicely placed back against her own sex. SKYHIGH ADDA (6) made it two wins in a row with her resuming success at Bunbury and will be fitter for that. Was Group 1 placed behind WISHING BELLE the last time they clashed last season and the draw inside that rival will aid her. LIVY ANN (1) has been coming from wider or second line barriers so will enjoy the ace draw and usually races well here. NOT SO SWEET (10) steps up in grade off her resuming maiden win but she draws for a trail and has some upside so is worth including along with CRUNCHNSIP (2) who placed behind WISHING BELLE last start and draws well.",
